pull.title: update bitcoin_en.ts (translation master file) to match current master branch as of 2012-05-09
pull.body:
I would like to do this now regularly, to make our translations faster and better!

That file is generated via:
"lupdate -no-obsolete bitcoin\bitcoin-qt.pro"
